{"type": "article", "id": 418, "title": "来看小动物 Selfie，超萌！", "description": "", "date": "2014-05-13T15:22:16Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 514, "name": "国家地理"}, {"id": 7, "name": "艺术"}, {"id": 64, "name": "广告"}, {"id": 419, "name": "创意"}], "category": 12, "column": null, "author": 6, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604214528YojvLlXaqUFIWzOe.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t为了推广国家地理杂志的最新野生动物专题，艺术家 Silvio Medeiros 与 Diomedia Stock Photos Brazil 合作了一组幽默又萌的<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/art/wildlife-selfies-silvio-medeiros-national-geographic-05-12-2014/\" target=\"_blank\">广告片</a>，电梯里的熊猫、盥洗池前的大猩猩、梳妆镜前的考拉统统在自拍。这组广告同时想告诉人们即便在这个 Selfie 时代，我们仍然可以生产出好的图片，我们的手机都有很好的摄像头，人人都可以是摄影师。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604214526cblTJ1YiRasfVnyU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604214527aSkRjbluptxny7H4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606042145279gx4emjZO5Kh0WaL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}